s/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a5403a91e2581fe606138c653384e42be15832","tid":106833,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:57:24.000Z","msg":"humble bundle usd12 for warhammer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  wait for long time"},{"pid":"31089d06963b015e127a17fc385896edf9b16795","tid":106833,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個人喜歡Empire&gt;Napoleon=Shogun 2&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;others <br />\n應該少連登仔會揀Empire?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEmpire對我來講係未完成品<br />\nUI，wealth  system都唔成熟<br />\n個port &lt;==&gt; town wealth 系統  <br />\n廠商完全無點提<br />\n最後由hardcore fans研究左份攻略<br />\nport wealth點影響town wealth growth<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個海戰話咩T shape戰術   其實無咩用   到最後都係鬥rate<br />\nfirst rate &gt; second &gt; thrid &gt; ....<br />\n個D咩打頭  打尾    會爆   <br />\n其實無咩用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陸戰就更加<br />\n馬匹十分無用<br />\n最後都係skirmish mode 分散既游擊槍兵<br />\n鬥射完場<br />\n大炮 = 無用，只用來打穿牆<br />\n如果用auto resolve攻城，大炮都可以唔出</blockquote><br />\n好似有info 講port +幾多growth<br />\n海戰次次都自動波算 反正都係睇士氣同本身數據 冇乜戰術<br />\n大炮去到napolean 先有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大範圍果陣炮又冇用 散射又reload 慢 射一兩下人地都近戰 或者隔住條河個d lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n騎兵有用但打唔贏列兵/擲彈兵 最多用黎追擊低士氣/打炮兵/爆菊花"},{"pid":"506638cf8a2e8d62a4359ebf017274927b1d2e4c","tid":106833,"uid":75139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:31:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個人喜歡Empire&amp;gt;Napoleon=Shogun 2&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&amp;gt;others <br />\n應該少連登仔會揀Empire?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEmpire支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得最正應該係napoleon既炮兵+戰鬥系統+ 外交系統+ 間碟系統 其他溝empire 大地圖+傳教+回復系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3cf356da6a92bf715aa358b3f0fcd079b5a5386","tid":106833,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"幕府玩左好耐，反而戰鎚一陣就放低左代入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b4aa6b5d8574fec0d5d23347f34248d4e5508f","tid":106833,"uid":23026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:06:54.000Z","msg":"個人認為，其實幕府玩法真係最簡單"},{"pid":"9d0893abf53c2ff4aee062648f7c4baac72e97f0","tid":106833,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人認為，其實幕府玩法真係最簡單</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n然後Empire 係簡陋<br />\n<br />\n利申買齊，淨係玩左shogun同empire,而家開 medieval 畫面好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但睇落好豐富，有冇人可以講下中世界點解咁多人鐘意等看代入下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737f0fd5416cff8cea7a621e513239168c7d8cf5","tid":106833,"uid":67432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:05:11.000Z","msg":"睇就覺得好玩 上手應該好撚難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313bc5a77ecac021248eafb46f812aa4953203d4","tid":106833,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T03:18:11.000Z","msg":"Medieval <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次玩用土耳其，食撚左成個拜占庭，俾蒙古屌屎忽加十字軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴撚線"},{"pid":"6d431f5ad27b4cfefc82672b385a6ae4cebee536","tid":106833,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T03:19:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Medieval <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次玩用土耳其，食撚左成個拜占庭，俾蒙古屌屎忽加十字軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴撚線</blockquote><br />\n最錯係一開始由得開羅俾人東征左，英格蘭起下面打上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三面俾人打"},{"pid":"7979f5d22117c6b569b75d59317b503daceb6a9e","tid":106833,"uid":60967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T04:33:49.000Z","msg":"羅馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fe137f9685c221344c67e940c5c7cab320f108","tid":106833,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個人認為，其實幕府玩法真係最簡單</blockquote><br />\n幕府先好玩 <br />\n先唔講冇第二隻game有得玩源平合戰 / 幕未<br />\n本身戰國都好玩 夠簡單 但又有挑戰性 打到咁上下就會比人圍攻<br />\n最敗筆係冇咩歷史事件 同 史實武將 但玩落都完勝信長野望"}]}